stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> uploaded : 📤 管理员上传文件

    uploaded --> parsing : ▶️ 触发解析任务
    parsing --> parsed : ✅ 解析成功
    parsing --> failed : ❌ 解析失败

    parsed --> cleaning : 文本清洗
    cleaning --> splitting : 文本切分
    splitting --> embedding : Embedding 向量化
    embedding --> indexing : 写入向量索引

    indexing --> pending_review : ✅ 索引完成，待审核
    indexing --> failed : ❌ 索引失败

    pending_review --> published : ✅ 审核通过
    pending_review --> rejected : ❌ 审核驳回

    rejected --> uploaded : 🔄 修改后重新上传
    failed --> uploaded : 🔄 修复后重试

    published --> offline : 📴 手动下线
    offline --> published : 🔄 重新上线

    published --> [*]